{"data": [{"id": "4745738", "title": "Goldman Sachs BDC: This Is Not A BDC You Want To Have Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"girl balancing on red rope with arms outstretched\" data-id=\"2150983341\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In December 2023, I issued my first <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659842-goldman-sachs-bdc-signs-structural-underperformance-going-forward\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659842-goldman-sachs-bdc-signs-structural-underperformance-going-forward\" target=\"_blank\">article </a>Goldman Sachs BDC (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GSBD\" title=\"Goldman Sachs BDC\">GSBD</a></span>), plotting a rather bearish thesis. The title of the article captured the essence nicely: <em>Goldman Sachs BDC: Signs Of Structural Underperformance Going Forward</em>. The key message</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745738-goldman-sachs-bdc-this-is-not-a-bdc-you-want-to-have-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 17:15:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4744760", "title": "Very Bad News For REITs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Newspaper Headlines Bad News\" data-id=\"174071285\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1430px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Liliboas</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Before going into this update, please note that I am not trying to be political. There are pros and cons to both parties and their proposed policies, and I am simply analyzing how these policies could affect various REITs. Thank you for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744760-very-bad-news-for-reits", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 17:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745786", "title": "The Next Big Theme: December 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman holding glowing light bulb with shows light bulb with bank icons outline,finance and banking digital, Finance and banking networks, Digital marketing, cyber security, Business technology.\" data-id=\"1498729115\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"688px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bussarin Rinchumrus/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>U.S. Infrastructure</h2> <p><em>Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act Funds Flow to More Projects</em></p> <p>On November 15, the third anniversary of the signing of the Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act, the U.S. Department of Transportation (DOT) announced over $3.4 billion in grants</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745786-the-next-big-theme-december-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:20:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745494", "title": "10 Stocks I'm Buying As REITs Have Never Looked So Good", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate investment trust REIT. Finacial concept 2022\" data-id=\"1370094487\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Funtap</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The market's sharp selloff over the past week puzzled me at first.</p> <p>It seemed to have been triggered by the Fed's changed \"dot plot\" forecast from three rate cuts next year to two. Was that enough to cause such a selloff?</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745494-10-stocks-im-buying-as-reits-have-never-looked-so-good", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:05:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745714", "title": "Weekly Indicators: USD, Commodities, New Orders Face Plant Even As Yield Curve Normalizes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy banks going over a cliff\" data-id=\"1072593736\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Purpose</h2> <p>I look at the <strong>high frequency weekly indicators</strong> because while they can be very noisy, they provide a good nowcast of the economy, and will telegraph the maintenance or change in the economy well before monthly or quarterly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745714-weekly-indicators-usd-commodities-new-orders-face-plant-even-as-yield-curve-normalizes", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745782", "title": "Is SolarEdge At Its Final Edge?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"engineering technician Setting up the solar panel inverter in the electrical room Service engineer installs solar cells on factory roofs Concept of clean energy and renewable energy\" data-id=\"2166408868\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Eakarat Buanoi/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The fall from the Olympus in 2023-2024 for SolarEdge (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SEDG\" title=\"SolarEdge Technologies, Inc.\">SEDG</a></span>) has been abrupt and bloody. Not if it was something new for the solar energy sector: the 2011 to 2012 period was as cruel, if not more so; 2016 and 2018 were not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745782-is-solaredge-at-its-final-edge", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 15:16:15", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745780", "title": "Glaukos: Still Bullish, But Embedded Expectations Are Now High", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Update</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4632479-glaukos-continued-growth-rates-regulatory-tailwinds-and-support\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4632479-glaukos-continued-growth-rates-regulatory-tailwinds-and-support\" target=\"_blank\">my last publication</a> on Glaukos Corporation (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GKOS#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GKOS#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">GKOS</a>) in August FY'23 the stock is +90% and taken out additional price objectives along the way. The business is now valued &gt;12x book and 9x EV/IC as investors realize the value of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745780-glaukos-still-bullish-but-embedded-expectations-are-now-high", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 15:04:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745779", "title": "Sable Offshore Offers Convexity For 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/dv789006/photo/brent-oil-field-production-platforms-north-sea-uk.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=VCeNmxZhtV4kmeNv_LstvGNI9UIMFgAhcRVXxRwuM9A=\" alt=\"Brent Oil Field, Production Platforms, North Sea, UK\" data-id=\"dv789006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael Saint Maur Sheil/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Sable Offshore (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SOC\" title=\"Sable Offshore Corp.\">SOC</a></span>) is a risky former SPAC that holds the rights to an oil production complex off the coa